
Usage
-----

mkdir -p htmldir
cd htmldir
stagit path-to-repo


Install
-------
$ make
# doas make install


Dependencies
------------
- libgit2 (v0.22+).
- C compiler
- make


Features
--------

- Log and diffstat per commit.
- Show file tree.
- Detect README and LICENSE file to make a webpage.
- Atom feed git log.
- Make index page for multiple repositories.
